"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-08-13-olympic-volunteer-found-next-partners-corpse-hours-closing-ceremony-21413907\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Avolunteerfor theOlympic Gameshas been arrested for the alleged killing of his girlfriend after the closing ceremony inParis.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 125, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A 21-year-old woman who is thought to be Polish was found in the flat the couple shared in the touristy area of Montmartre in the French capital.\", \"from\": 127, \"to\": 272, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 239, \"end\": 249, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Montmartre\", \"score\": 0.9999775614374359, \"rank\": 2.2439065975331494e-05, \"text\": \"Montmartre\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Montmartre\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Montmartre\"}, {\"begin\": 257, \"end\": 263, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"score\": 0.8996087259499695, \"rank\": 0.10917222135198196, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She was reported as missing just after 7pm on Monday, just a day after the 33rd Games came to an end.\", \"from\": 274, \"to\": 375, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The couple, who have not been named, both spent weeks helping visitors to the sporting event, which took over most of Paris.\", \"from\": 377, \"to\": 501, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 495, \"end\": 500, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999358806, \"rank\": 6.4132610210668e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Police broke into their accommodation in the early hours of today and found her body, which had a blood clot on the left cheek, and traces of blood around the neck.\", \"from\": 503, \"to\": 667, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Her boyfriend was in the same room, and described by the officers as being 'in a semi-comatose state' after taking drugs and alcohol.\", \"from\": 669, \"to\": 802, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A spokesperson for prosecutors said: 'An investigation into voluntary homicide has been entrusted to the second district of the Paris judicial police after the discovery of the lifeless body of a young woman, aged 21, in an apartment in the 18th arrondissement.'\", \"from\": 804, \"to\": 1066, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 932, \"end\": 937, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999358806, \"rank\": 6.4132610210668e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He said her boyfriend has been wanted since Monday after the victim was reported as missing.\", \"from\": 1068, \"to\": 1160, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Enquiries established she was last seen at 1am on Sunday night, after taking part in the Olympics closing ceremony.\", \"from\": 1162, \"to\": 1277, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Her phone was geolocated to a suburb north of Paris and then - at around 11pm - her mother in Poland said they had received a text message from a friend saying the partner had done 'something stupid'.\", \"from\": 1279, \"to\": 1479, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1325, \"end\": 1330, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999358806, \"rank\": 6.4132610210668e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1373, \"end\": 1379, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland\", \"score\": 0.8905538513609783, \"rank\": 0.11516113254248819, \"text\": \"Poland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resour